  "title": "Westminster Shorter Q102",
  "body": "What do we pray for in the second petition?\n\nIn the second petition, which is, 'Thy kingdom come,' we pray, That Satan's kingdom may be destroyed; and that the kingdom of grace may be advanced, ourselves and others brought into it, and kept in it; and that the kingdom of glory may be hastened.",
